"""Check lint.assert_parameter_prior_type_is_valid."""
lint.assert_parameter_prior_type_is_valid(pd.DataFrame({
    INITIALIZATION_PRIOR_TYPE: [UNIFORM, LAPLACE, ''], OBJECTIVE_PRIOR_TYPE:
    [NORMAL, LOG_NORMAL, '']}))

    lint.assert_parameter_prior_type_is_valid(pd.DataFrame({
        INITIALIZATION_PRIOR_TYPE: ['normel']}))
